		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="439" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">风役人施放一连串的风弹，进行至多3段的连续攻击，对敌人分别造成<span color="#7fffd7">50%x3,50%x3,60%x5</span><span>伤害，第三段攻击带有追踪性；攻击造成的伤害带有(1,0.5,0.25,0.1)的衰减。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="479" width="424" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">风役人展开风嶂，当敌人对其施放攻击时，<span color="#ffbfbf">无视此次伤害</span><span>并发动反击：闪现至敌人上方投下权杖，造成</span><span color="#7fffd7">70%</span><span>伤害，并在此处再次产生一次较弱的风泽域，造成</span><span color="#7fffd7">100%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="767" width="1110" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">风役人瞄准目标，<span color="#ffebbf">消耗2%生命值</span><span>，2s后发动攻击，对目标敌人降下翠叶之诀，造成</span><span color="#7fffd7">90%</span><span>伤害并施加生命之契，随后发动追加「猎杀」攻击：<br/>翠叶之诀的场地将产生爆炸，造成</span><span color="#7fffd7">100%</span><span>伤害并施加生命之契。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/雪奈茨芙娜的蝶安奈拉.assets/Image_13.png')" x="720" y="137">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/雪奈茨芙娜的蝶安奈拉.assets/Image_14.png')" x="720" y="393">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/雪奈茨芙娜的蝶安奈拉.assets/Image_15.png')" x="720" y="681">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/雪奈茨芙娜的蝶安奈拉.assets/Image_16.png')" x="1392" y="137">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="439" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">风役人旋转权杖，进行一段重击，在敌人的下方连续产生3次的风泽域，均造成<span color="#7fffd7">100%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="899" y="62" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#00ae83" width="207" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" color="#00ae83">制图@Csxylic米游社</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/雪奈茨芙娜的蝶安奈拉.assets/Image_17.png')" x="68" y="64" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="1410" y="479" width="424" height="172" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">风役人的元素爆发命中所累加的生命之契大小等同于自身<span color="#ff9999">16%</span><span>的攻击力，且在该生命之契的影响下，目标敌人将每秒流失</span><span color="#dfbfff">(0.4%HP+72)</span><span>的生命值(后台停5%)，其与生命之契同生共死，持续10min。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
