		<RichText x="738" y="990" width="1094" height="62" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="32" fontWeight="bold" color="#bfffdf">固有天赋·佞意<span fontSize="24" color="#ffffff">：元素爆发的追加攻击对附有生命之契的目标造成的伤害提升</span><span fontSize="24" color="#ff9999">150%</span><span fontSize="24" color="#ffffff">。被施加生命之契的目标，在遭受每段追加「猎杀」时都会累积生命之契。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="739" y="894" width="1112" height="62" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="32" fontWeight="bold" color="#bfffdf">固有天赋·残枝<span fontSize="24" color="#ffffff">：爆发的第一段伤害命中时，</span><span fontSize="24" color="#ffebbf">恢复5%生命值</span><span fontSize="24" color="#ffffff">；生命值</span><span fontSize="24" color="#ffebbf">低于20%</span><span fontSize="24" color="#ffffff">时，施放元素爆发改为</span><span fontSize="24" color="#ffebbf">消耗10%当前生命值</span><span fontSize="24" color="#ffffff">。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
	</Group>
</Graphic>